{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_10_02",
  "title": "井川葵",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "話は分かった。……けど、今の話の中に\n俺の質問への答えは、なかったと思うんだけど",
      "startTime": 5.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、忘れてた。そういえばトリエルとのバトルで\nあの曲をうまく出来た理由だったっけ",
      "startTime": 13.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 17.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん説明するつもりだったよ。この話には\n続きがあるんだ。時間も遅いし、帰りながら話すよ",
      "startTime": 20.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "今、「忘れてた」って言ったよな？\n……まぁいい。続きを聞かせてくれ",
      "startTime": 28.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――『Grab the BIG4』開催中",
      "startTime": 33.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening",
      "startTime": 34.7000058492
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "驚いたな……あれから数日しか経ってないのに\n新曲の振り付け、だいぶ出来上がってるじゃないか",
      "startTime": 40.1333381653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "振り付けを作ったり、個人練習をするくらいしか\nやることがないんだよ",
      "startTime": 46.5333381653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "僕は活動休止中の身だからね\n……振り付けは四人分出来てるけど、見てみる？",
      "startTime": 52.1333381653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、もちろんだ。ぜひ見せてくれ\n……それにしても、安心したよ",
      "startTime": 60.100004832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "今の僕を見て、よく安心出来るね。あ、もしかして\n僕がやる気をなくして、ゴロゴロしてると思ってた？",
      "startTime": 68.900004832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうじゃない。葵は練習も振り付けも好きだって\n知ってるから、そんなことは心配してないよ",
      "startTime": 76.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺が安心したのは、四人分の振り付けを作ってたことだ\nそれって、リズノワを辞めるつもりはないってことだろ",
      "startTime": 84.8333381653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "……別に。他にやることがないからね\n気分転換にやってるだけだよ",
      "startTime": 92.6666714986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "大体、こんなに調子を落としてる僕が\nいつリズノワに戻れるかなんて、分からない",
      "startTime": 98.9333381653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん達は\nいつでも戻って来てほしいと思ってるんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 103.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "うん。莉央達なら、今のこんな僕でも歓迎してくれる\nそれは僕にだって分かる",
      "startTime": 113.3333381653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、みんなの優しさに甘えて、今戻ってしまったら\n僕が僕を許せなくなるから",
      "startTime": 120.9666714986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "……なんて偉そうなことを言ってるけど\nスランプ脱出の目処は全然ついてないんだ",
      "startTime": 127.800004832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "今の僕が、この振り付けで踊っても\n納得のいくものには全然ならないよ",
      "startTime": 135.000004832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "それに、今作ってるこの振り付け自体\nもっといいものに出来るはずなんだ。なのに……",
      "startTime": 141.5333432515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……葵、一つ提案なんだが\nその振り付け、莉央さんに見せてみたらどうだ？",
      "startTime": 149.0333432515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんなら、もっといいものにするために\n意見を出してくれるんじゃないか",
      "startTime": 155.7000221252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "え……でも自分の都合でリズノワから離れた僕が\nそんなことをするのは……",
      "startTime": 164.1333554585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんにどう思われるか、気になるのか？\nそんなことを気にするなんて、葵らしくないな",
      "startTime": 170.6333554585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "……なんだよ、僕らしくないって\n僕はこう見えて結構気配りの人なんだけど",
      "startTime": 178.8666887919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ははっ、それはすまなかったな\nでも、いい振り付けにしたいんだろ？",
      "startTime": 186.2666887919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そのためなら他人の顔色なんて気にしない\n自分のやりたいことをやるのが井川葵じゃないのか？",
      "startTime": 192.6000221252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "……知った風なことを言われるのは好きじゃないけど\n{user}君の言う通りだ",
      "startTime": 202.0000221252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "似合わないことを言っちゃったね。面と向かって言って\nくれてありがとう。後で録画して、莉央に送ってみるよ",
      "startTime": 208.3666887919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 214.7500249226
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 214.7500249226
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、そんな話もしたな。その後は聞いてないけど\n莉央さんから返事はあったのか？",
      "startTime": 221.3228498249,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "うん、あった。そしてそれが、君が知りたがってた\n理由だよ。……あれ、もしかして通じてない？",
      "startTime": 228.0000221252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 234.3000249226
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "『Grab the BIG4』のセミファイナルで\nいいパフォーマンスが出来た理由なんだけど",
      "startTime": 237.0000050862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "（理由……ど、どういうことだ？）\n（葵の言ってることが全然分からない……）",
      "startTime": 244.1666717529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 247.233358256
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi019.m4a",
      "text": "僕の言ってること、全然分からないって顔してるね\n仕方ないな。じゃあ説明してあげる。特別にね",
      "startTime": 252.9333554585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi020.m4a",
      "text": "あの日、君のアドバイスを受けて\n振り付けの映像を莉央に送ったんだ",
      "startTime": 260.9333595275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 263.4666956583
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
